b'Areas of Impact'
b'From preparing the next generation of physicians for practice to providing critical medical services, philanthropy allows us to fortify our mission and continually improve our educational programming, our community involvement and our partnerships. A gift in support of the transformational changes happening today helps position the College of Medicine Rockford as a leader in the training and development of the next generation of healthcare providers who will positively impact our community \xe2\x80\x93 both economically and through the delivery of high-quality patient care to our community.'
b'The following are giving opportunities where your gift can have significant impact:'
